= I18n =

The official translator of the project is [[http://www.translationproject.org|Translation Project]]. The translation domain status can be found [[http://www.translationproject.org/domain/xkeyboard-config.html|here]]. The up-to-date list of .po files is available [[http://translationproject.org/latest/xkeyboard-config/|here]].

