= Submission rules =

There are certain rules in the project. These rules are applied to all contributed layouts/variants/models/option. These rules are simple to follow. The code which does not follow them is rejected (or the author is asked to fix the issues). The rules are listed [[Software/XKeyboardConfig/Rules|here]]
